      <title>欧洲加息势头消退，投资银行家占据上风</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/investment-bankers-carry-the-day-as-rate-boost-fades-in-europe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于受益于金融市场的波动，投资银行家们弥补了预期的利息收入放缓，再次成为欧洲银行收益中的明星。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/investment-bankers-carry-the-day-as-rate-boost-fades-in-europe</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 16:03:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>关税忧虑和美国经济走强导致美元下跌预期短暂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/dollar-drop-seen-brief-amid-tariff-worries-us-economic-strength</link>
      <description><![CDATA[交易员们押注，鉴于美国经济相对强劲以及对贸易战风险的担忧挥之不去，美元周二的暴跌可能是短暂的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/dollar-drop-seen-brief-amid-tariff-worries-us-economic-strength</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 16:00:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国职位空缺降至 9 月以来最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-04/us-job-openings-fall-to-lowest-since-september-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国 12 月职位空缺数量下降幅度超过预期，降至三个月以来的最低水平，这与劳动力市场逐渐放缓的趋势一致。美国劳工统计局职位空缺和劳动力流动调查 (JOLTS) 周二显示，可用职位数量从 11 月修订后的 816 万个降至 760 万个。彭博社的 Michael McKee 报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-04/us-job-openings-fall-to-lowest-since-september-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 15:40:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>ADM 考虑剥离资产以精简投资组合</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/adm-plans-to-cut-jobs-as-profits-head-for-third-year-of-declines</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于面临利润下滑，阿彻丹尼尔斯米德兰公司正在考虑剥离资产，作为削减成本计划的一部分。]]></description>
