      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 13:01:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>咖啡价格有望因供应问题创下 45 年来最长涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/coffee-set-for-longest-gaining-streak-in-45-years-on-supply-woes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于市场正在努力解决主要种植区持续存在的供应问题，咖啡价格有望创下 1980 年以来最长的上涨势头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/coffee-set-for-longest-gaining-streak-in-45-years-on-supply-woes</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 12:39:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国反击美国关税后欧洲天然气价格下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/europe-gas-prices-fall-after-china-hits-back-against-us-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在中国对包括液化天然气在内的一系列商品征收关税以反击美国关税之后，欧洲天然气价格结束了连续五个交易日的上涨，这可能为欧洲买家提供更多燃料。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/europe-gas-prices-fall-after-china-hits-back-against-us-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 08:06:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中美贸易战冲击美元走低 铜价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/copper-and-zinc-climb-as-trump-delays-tariffs-on-canada-mexico</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普对中国商品征收 10% 的关税，而北京方面也采取了一系列措施予以回应，美元走低导致铜价上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/copper-and-zinc-climb-as-trump-delays-tariffs-on-canada-mexico</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 01:25:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普发起对华贸易战 黄金价格创下新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/gold-holds-near-record-high-as-tariff-confusion-aids-haven-bids</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普对中国征收 10% 的关税，引发北京方面迅速采取报复措施，提振了避险需求，金价由此升至历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/gold-holds-near-record-high-as-tariff-confusion-aids-haven-bids</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 00:15:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
